text: Efflatounaria is a genus of soft corals in the family Xeniidae. ==Species== The World Register of Marine Species lists the following species: *Efflatounaria alba Verseveldt, 1977 *Efflatounaria nana Hickson, 1931 *Efflatounaria tottoni Gohar, 1939 == References == Category:Anthozoa genera Category:Xeniidae
title: Efflatounaria
